OL,3,CChristian Eriksen 'close to leaving
OL,4,Chospital' after collapse during match
OL,6,FChristian Eriksen is "in good spirits"
OL,7,Fand close to being discharged, the
OL,8,FDanish team's doctor has said, after
OL,9,Fthe footballer collapsed while playing
OL,10,Ffor Denmark on Sunday.
OL,12,FEriksen was seen putting his hand to
OL,13,Fhis chest in the 65th minute of the
OL,14,Finternational friendly against Ukraine
OL,15,Fin Odense, Denmark, before he fell to
OL,16,Fthe ground and had to be treated by
OL,17,Fmedics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
