OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780966989
OL,3,CChristian Eriksen 'close to leaving
OL,4,Chospital' after collapse during match
OL,6,FThe former Tottenham and Manchester
OL,7,FUnited player regained consciousness
OL,8,Fat the scene and was able to walk off
OL,9,Fthe pitch himself, and was then taken
OL,10,Fto hospital.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
