FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780966989
OL,3,CChristian Eriksen 'close to leaving
OL,4,Chospital' after collapse during match
OL,6,F"I spoke to Christian this morning and
OL,7,Fhe is doing well. He is with his
OL,8,Ffamily and in good spirits," the
OL,9,Fteam's doctor, Morten Boesen, said in
OL,10,Fa short statement shared by the Danish
OL,11,FFootball Association.
OL,13,F"The expectation is that he will be
OL,14,Fdischarged soon and can go home.
OL,16,F"We are taking good care of the
OL,17,Fplayers and staff and are in contact
OL,18,Fwith them on an ongoing basis."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
