PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780966989
OL,3,CChristian Eriksen 'close to leaving
OL,4,Chospital' after collapse during match
OL,6,FEriksen previously suffered a cardiac
OL,7,Farrest and had to be resuscitated on
OL,8,Fthe pitch during Denmark's opening
OL,9,FEuropean Championship group game
OL,10,Fagainst Finland in 2021.
OL,12,FHe was fitted with an Implantable
OL,13,FCardioverter Defibrillator (ICD),
OL,14,Fwhich Boesen said on Sunday appeared
OL,15,Fto be "functioning as it should",
OL,16,Fallowing the footballer to regain
OL,17,Fconsciousness "very quickly".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
