FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780966989
OL,3,CChristian Eriksen 'close to leaving
OL,4,Chospital' after collapse during match
OL,6,F"We were able to communicate with him
OL,7,Fright away. He will now undergo
OL,8,Ffurther examination at the hospital to
OL,9,Fdetermine what caused the incident,"
OL,10,Fthe doctor said after the match.
OL,12,FThe ICD - described by Boesen as a
OL,13,Fpacemaker - allowed Eriksen to
OL,14,Fcontinue his football career.
OL,16,FThe 2021 collapse shocked fans around
OL,17,Fthe world, as several medics had to
OL,18,Fgive Eriksen chest compressions on the
OL,19,Fpitch while his teammates formed a
OL,20,Fcircle around him to shield the scene
OL,21,Ffrom public view.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
